trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator.OnTypeGenerated"></xref> event.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.TypeGeneratedEventArgs"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.TypeGeneratedEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified source and base type.
The source of the type.
The base type.
Gets a `List(CodeAttributeDeclaration)` containing the attributes that will be added to the type.
The members are added after the <xref:System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator.OnTypeGenerated> event is raised
A collection that contains the attributes that will be added to the type.
The collection is empty if no attributes will be added to the type.
Gets a `List(Type)` containing the interfaces that will be added to the type.
The members are added after the <xref:System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator.OnTypeGenerated> event is raised.
A collection that contains the interfaces that will be added to the type.
The collection is empty if no interfaces will be added.
Gets a `List(CodeTypeMember)` containing the members that will be added to the type.
The members are added after the <xref:System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator.OnTypeGenerated> event is raised.
A collection that contains the members that will be added to the type.
The collection is empty if no members will be added.
Gets or sets the base type.
The base type.

The default is <xref href="System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.EntityObject"></xref>, <xref href="System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.ComplexObject"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext"></xref>, depending on the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.TypeGeneratedEventArgs.TypeSource"></xref> property value.
Gets the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.GlobalItem"></xref> object that is the source of the type.
The <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.GlobalItem"></xref> object that is the source of the type.
